---
title: Coconut Chicken Curry with lentils and coriander cauliflower rice
description: This chicken curry is creamy and rich, but it's also got plenty of healthy elements to shout about. Protein and fibre filled lentils are a great addition to any meal, while cauliflower acts as a substitute side for more starchy white rice.
